{"tid":903998,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Tim Bourton執導《小飛象》真人版電影正式預告上線","createTime":"2018-11-16T03:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T08:51:54.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bc76c58a1a0b16cad9e8a8e208a3b0cf4abd9662","tid":903998,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:51:14.000Z","msg":"從《黑魔女：沈睡魔咒》（Maleficent）、《仙履奇緣》（Cinderella）開始，迪士尼影業大概一年會帶來一部經典動畫改編真人版電影，不過隨著製作計畫越來越密集，後續也將有更多作品等著要與觀眾見面，其中將在明年春天登場的《小飛象》（Dumbo）寫實版電影也在今天釋出了正式版預告。<br />\n此片由提姆波頓（Tim Bourton）執導，《變形金剛》（Transformers）系列電影編劇厄倫克魯格（Ehren Kruger）執筆劇本，內容描述前馬戲團明星霍特在從戰場回來後，生活變得一團亂，因此馬戲團主人麥斯找他來幫忙照顧一隻因為擁有大耳朵而成為笑柄的象寶寶。然而在他的孩子發現小象會飛之後，一名能言善道的企業家開始把小象當作表演明星。<br />\n《小飛象》主演卡司包括伊娃葛林（Eva Green）、米高基頓（Michael Keaton）、丹尼迪維托（Danny DeVito）、柯林法洛（Colin Farrell）等，將於 2019 年 3 月 29 日上映。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/c8eKVxooKCw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fc8eKVxooKCw&d=cVkKFaQom%2Bj3qDTSP7JoTUjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=bb944ad2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/c8eKVxooKCw</a>"},{"pid":"aef3eb46b561b1602700873d06375ca5f2609b6b","tid":903998,"uid":4420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:54:38.000Z","msg":"Eva Green<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04496dc71610f93461c0e31efe0177afafa70cd","tid":903998,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2526d88d6bf19eaeba5333c908867dc15048f7ac","tid":903998,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b04496dc71610f93461c0e31efe0177afafa70cd","tid":903998,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj